source.name: Maryland Female Population for Ages 16+ Projections: 1970-2040
source.description:
Historical and Projected Female Population 16+ in Maryland and its Jurisdictions: 1970-2040.
Projected numbers are rounded to the nearest 10.
Prepared by the Maryland Department of Planning, April 2012.
